Class Seats

  • java.lang.Object
    • assignment.AccountableObject
      • assignment.AbstractNoNullList<Seat>
        • assignment.Seats
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Seat>, java.util.Collection<Seat>, java.util.List<Seat>

    public class Seats
extends AbstractNoNullList<Seat>
implements java.io.Serializable
    Resizable-array implementation of the List interface for Seat objects. Implements all optional list operations, and permits all elements, excluding null.
    Author:
    Graham Fairweather
    See Also:
    AbstractNoNullList, Serialized Form
